# ── Compiled Go binaries ───────────────────────────────────────
# Rebuilt on every `go build`; server.old*.exe are historical snapshots
# from past restarts. All regenerable; not tracked.
server.exe
server.new.exe
server.new.exe~
server*.exe
bin/*.exe
bin/mediamtx
bin/mediamtx_runtime.yml
bin/mediamtx.log

# ── AI model weights ───────────────────────────────────────────
# PyTorch checkpoints are 10-120 MB each and should live in a model
# registry (S3, HuggingFace, or a download script), not git. If a model
# needs to be versioned alongside code, use Git LFS.
*.pt
*.safetensors
*.bin
*.onnx

# ── Build cache ────────────────────────────────────────────────
frontend/tsconfig.tsbuildinfo
*.tsbuildinfo

# Windows build / install scratch
build.bat
mediamtx.zip

# ── Logs ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────
*.log
server_*.log
frontend_*.log
backend*.log
frontend_error.log
frontend_output.log

# ── Node / Next.js ─────────────────────────────────────────────
frontend/node_modules/
frontend/.next/
frontend/out/
frontend/.vercel/
frontend/.turbo/
frontend/.env.local
frontend/.env.*.local

# ── Go build cache / test coverage ─────────────────────────────
coverage.out
*.test
*.prof

# ── Secrets ────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# .env is gitignored; .env.example is committed as the template.
.env
.env.*
!.env.example

# ── Storage scratch ────────────────────────────────────────────
# Video segments / HLS / exports / thumbnails all live at /data
# (Docker volumes) or ./storage/ in dev. Never committed.
storage/
data/
recordings/

# ── Editor + OS junk ───────────────────────────────────────────
.vscode/
.idea/
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
*.swp
*~

# ── Misc session artefacts ─────────────────────────────────────
cam_snapshot.jpg
clear_db.go.bak
*.bak
